queries.sql: SELECT DATE(tanggal_acara) as date, COUNT(*) as total_events, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'dikonfirmasi' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as confirmed, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'diproses' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as processed, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'selesai' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as completed FROM `pesanan` WHERE DATE(tanggal_acara) >= '2025-11-01' AND DATE(tanggal_acara) <= '2025-11-30' AND `status` IN ('dikonfirmasi','diproses','selesai') GROUP BY DATE(tanggal_acara)
